{"tid":1285848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢連日示威","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T19:16:15.000Z","uid":200851,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bfee8588ef7650451f80116cc24798a833e409","tid":1285848,"uid":200851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"【還我綠水青山】武漢連日來萬人上街 抗議政府強建垃圾焚化廠<br />\n<br />\n湖北武漢新洲區陽邏開發區連續多日有數以萬計的市民上街遊行示威，抗議政府在人口密集地區興建垃圾焚燒發電廠。<br />\n<br />\n網上消息指，示威者圍堵武漢市政府門口後觸發警民衝突，警方在鎮壓清場時更有民眾被打至頭破血流。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2993192/org/a11dc82dc3b62ad99b3995bc2891464c.jpg/7fuiZED8pKDxI4u4LF0nseoYfKJgVDyHKeZuiSnmbok\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2993192%2Forg%2Fa11dc82dc3b62ad99b3995bc2891464c.jpg%2F7fuiZED8pKDxI4u4LF0nseoYfKJgVDyHKeZuiSnmbok&h=aa78fcfe&s={SIZE}\" /> （微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2993198/org/c7a0c9513c2ceac00643621a24c5ec23.jpg/lAqLCcItA-Jlqg4zL-OpPA2903If7RHIMX1htTF9YbU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2993198%2Forg%2Fc7a0c9513c2ceac00643621a24c5ec23.jpg%2FlAqLCcItA-Jlqg4zL-OpPA2903If7RHIMX1htTF9YbU&h=28c2864f&s={SIZE}\" /> （微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2993196/org/6dafb221b8990c895a3940107298f69c.jpg/kcIOwIG6m3PYBquENaaNarkdL8X0P49u_-Q87f_kPO0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2993196%2Forg%2F6dafb221b8990c895a3940107298f69c.jpg%2FkcIOwIG6m3PYBquENaaNarkdL8X0P49u_-Q87f_kPO0&h=57ce45f4&s={SIZE}\" /> （微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2993195/org/8a916f91a9dcb9c165d732eca7807d73.jpg/96RYjg2RaxjYdDmuXSVNppWjQyrf0rbvM8frejPH63o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2993195%2Forg%2F8a916f91a9dcb9c165d732eca7807d73.jpg%2F96RYjg2RaxjYdDmuXSVNppWjQyrf0rbvM8frejPH63o&h=d5e05a9f&s={SIZE}\" /> （微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2993197/org/83fe814173ddb2afaec11eae4de10e82.jpg/oIWKP3hSNzHeOvqdEOpjSJODJOtbVNmY417CheNewoU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2993197%2Forg%2F83fe814173ddb2afaec11eae4de10e82.jpg%2FoIWKP3hSNzHeOvqdEOpjSJODJOtbVNmY417CheNewoU&h=4ebcba1f&s={SIZE}\" /> （微博）<br />\n<br />\n據了解，陽邏市民在上月中旬得知政府計劃興建發電廠時，已有百多人自發聚集維權、派發傳單，有20多人事後一度被捕。有不具名市民稱，當地已有一個垃圾填埋場，所產生的惡臭覆蓋方圓8公里，嚴重影響數十萬人的生活。垃圾填埋場原定2020年到期關閉並改建成公園，「前段時間突然說要改成垃圾焚燒廠，所以居民們都不同意。」<br />\n<br />\n另一名市民則稱垃圾填埋場為禍陽邏十多年，空氣差、地下水質受污染，「現在又搞一個焚燒場，那不是污染更嚴重了，關係到我們生命安全了啊。」該名市民又透露，當地確多日來有數以萬計的市民遊行示威，由早到晚，範圍遍及主幹道、輕軌站及發電廠選址，不斷有人高呼「還我綠水青山」。<br />\n<br />\n公開資料顯示，陳家沖垃圾填埋場關閉後，按照市政府辦公廳要求，擬將在陳家沖循環經濟產業園內新建生活垃圾焚燒發電項目，設計處理規模為每天2000噸，目前正處於選址階段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2993193/org/65e32ce5a44d0f7c824fda8739a7618f.jpg/RkdywUcTkmJTfvF3yqrHi8hRoTFYsMx8nvRIop70SKI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2993193%2Forg%2F65e32ce5a44d0f7c824fda8739a7618f.jpg%2FRkdywUcTkmJTfvF3yqrHi8hRoTFYsMx8nvRIop70SKI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fb2355fc&s={SIZE}\" /> （微博）<br />\n<br />\n但值得一提是，網上有流傳一份新洲區政府的文件，內容指發電廠尚未啟動環評程序，更未立項及開工建設，「網上誤傳陳家沖垃圾焚燒發電廠動工工地，實際上並非垃圾焚燒發電項目，而是江北鐵路建設拆遷還建工程」。文件最後強調會堅持以人民為中心的發展思想，按照「群眾不同意，項目不開工」的原則嚴格依照法定程序，呼籲廣大市民不信謠、不傳謠。<br />\n<br />\n但事發至今當局極力封鎖消息，網上相關的圖片及片段被大量刪除，示威現場的網絡訊號據稱亦離奇地變得非常微弱。<br />\n<br />\n香港01: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/348307/%E9%82%84%E6%88%91%E7%B6%A0%E6%B0%B4%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E4%BE%86%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97-%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%B7%E5%BB%BA%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%84%9A%E5%8C%96%E5%BB%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F348307%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B1%25B1-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%2584%259A%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25BB%25A0&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRbCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=b553ed7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/348307/%E9%82%84%E6%88%91%E7%B6%A0%E6%B0%B4%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E4%BE%86%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97-%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%B7%E5%BB%BA%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%84%9A%E5%8C%96%E5%BB%A0</a><br />\n<br />\n反了 反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eca9fac87268626f61c85d228d6a2af1c2740d9","tid":1285848,"uid":200851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:05:38.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20190702/video/248842.html?%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%84%9A%E7%87%92%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%20%E7%88%86%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fb5%2F20190702%2Fvideo%2F248842.html%3F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%2584%259A%25E7%2587%2592%25E9%25A0%2585%25E7%259B%25AE%2520%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRbCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=fe8be863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20190702/video/248842.html?%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%84%9A%E7%87%92%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%20%E7%88%86%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81</a>"},{"pid":"d2a92b4e4b5482a136e91075f758ba9fc468ea8c","tid":1285848,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb0bf56fa3cadc5bb7afe18f14dc06c2e9b2a67","tid":1285848,"uid":83849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"正呀正呀，希望香港呢點星火可以係大陸燎原開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲早一日老共氣數漸盡"},{"pid":"0a4e03e2fa16810fa0ad5bc463bdfef3aa246d88","tid":1285848,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:19:41.000Z","msg":"隨意一睇<br />\n仲以為第3張望鏡頭果位係劉馬車"},{"pid":"304cd36a4863269f8b81265334b2220a28ee228d","tid":1285848,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"到底點樣先可以贏得到武力鎮壓"},{"pid":"061f60cd417a7d6dfd9c15546894a62c02e854b2","tid":1285848,"uid":200851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>[size=5]武漢民眾上街反對興建焚化爐　遭警暴力鎮壓[size=5]</strong><br />\n中國湖北省武漢市新洲區陽邏民眾，近日因為不滿當局興建大型垃圾焚化爐，連日來多次上街抗爭，其間多次爆發警民衝突。據網上流傳的影片、照片可見，有警員暴力驅散示威者，有人被打至頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n當地民眾因反對焚化爐項目，在6月28日、7月2日、3日持續爆發大規模抗議活動。中國官方連日來不斷封鎖消息，大陸媒體幾乎完全沒有報道事件。不過民眾將大量抗爭現場的影片上載網上，引起了網民的關注。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter上流傳的影片可見，陽邏居民連日的抗爭從白天持續到晚上，數以千名民眾擠滿馬路。當地市面出現大批防暴警察，有民眾坐在警方築起的人牆，阻止警方推進。另有影片顯示警察揮動警棍驅散示威者，片中隱約聽到小孩高喊「媽媽」，以及婦女高聲尖叫的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n網絡流傳的一份相信是陽邏當局發出的公開信，指焚化爐尚未啟動環評程式，更未立項和開工建設，網上誤傳發電廠動工實際上鐵路建設拆遷工程。公開信結尾又指，現在是一個公平、公正、公開的社會，互聯網資訊傳播也更加便利，政府和群眾的溝通應該更加通暢無協調，同時希望陽邏群眾一定要合理合法表達訴求，切不可非法集會起哄鬧事。<br />\n<br />\n網上亦流傳一個「黨員工作群」的微信截圖，指陽邏地區今晚實行宵禁，店面一律停止營業。惟本網未能證實消息真偽。<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞：<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%88%88%E5%BB%BA%E7%84%9A%E5%8C%96%E7%88%90-%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%2584%259A%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%2588%2590-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593%2F&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRbCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=409ec56a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%2584%259A%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%2588%2590-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593%2F&h=58bb76bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%88%88%E5%BB%BA%E7%84%9A%E5%8C%96%E7%88%90-%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93/</a><br />\n<br />\n支持立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a89d5bf4bfc6effb4e3e1ad0de8347f66c3413d","tid":1285848,"uid":264806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">起來 不願做奴隸的人們！</span>"},{"pid":"b2dab0bf2f6fa6fb8e421584589e3a3199274a0c","tid":1285848,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"偏地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c8d496e787bc1da9fdfebf0c87911fb2da330a","tid":1285848,"uid":76854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:41:15.000Z","msg":"幾時connect埋武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27aacc1a35468a582f01ce6c6339cff5d127d0b","tid":1285848,"uid":161168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}